setDetails.setDescription:
MoonQuant's ETH TrendBlazer combines two distinct engines for buys and sells with their own intrinsic logic. One seeks to identify possible bottoms and take advantage of long timeframe trends. The other engine will look for extensions and lock in winning trades. If the trend then continues it will restart the cycle. If a top is confirmed, it will revert and enable the other engine to identify a new bottom. 

MQE utilizes an AI self-learning parametrized channel, to avoid sideways trading. In these cases, there could be longer periods without trades. This algorithm searches for long term trends and can go many days without a trade. As it confirms trends, it will not act immediately on tops or bottoms but upon their confirmation. We think of it as an alternative to hodling, gaining some Beta on longer trades.

MQE is not a regulated investment vehicle and MoonQuant is not a regulated investment advisor. An investor may get back less than the amount invested.

Please note that MoonQuant or Token Sets reserve the right to amend the operation of the set.
